original_query: SELECT ph.UserId, c.UserId FROM comments as c, posts as p, postHistory as ph, badges as b, users as u WHERE u.Id = c.UserId AND u.Id = p.OwnerUserId AND u.Id = ph.UserId AND u.Id = b.UserId AND p.PostTypeId=1 AND p.Score<=35 AND p.AnswerCount=1 AND p.CommentCount<=17 AND p.FavoriteCount>=0 AND b.Date>=CAST('2010-07-27 17:58:45' AS TIMESTAMP) AND b.Date<=CAST('2014-09-06 17:33:22' AS TIMESTAMP) AND u.Views<=233 AND u.DownVotes<=2 AND u.CreationDate>=CAST('2010-09-16 16:00:55' AS TIMESTAMP) AND u.CreationDate<=CAST('2014-08-24 21:12:02' AS TIMESTAMP)
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT badges.userid AS E4_userid FROM badges AS badges WHERE badges.date >= TIMESTAMP '2010-07-27 17:58:45' AND badges.date <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-06 17:33:22'
CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT comments.userid AS E1_userid FROM comments AS comments
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_0 AS SELECT * FROM E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E1 WHERE E4.E4_userid=E1.E1_userid)
CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT posthistory.userid AS E3_userid FROM posthistory AS posthistory
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_1 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_0 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3 WHERE E4_stage1_0.E4_userid=E3.E3_userid)

CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT posts.owneruserid AS E2_owneruserid FROM posts AS posts WHERE CAST(posts.posttypeid AS INTEGER) = 1 AND posts.score <= 35 AND posts.answercount = 1 AND posts.commentcount <= 17 AND posts.favoritecount >= 0
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_2 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2 WHERE E4_stage1_1.E4_userid=E2.E2_owneruserid)

CREATE VIEW E5 AS SELECT users.id AS E5_id FROM users AS users WHERE users.views <= 233 AND users.downvotes <= 2 AND (users.creationdate >= TIMESTAMP '2010-09-16 16:00:55' AND users.creationdate <= TIMESTAMP '2014-08-24 21:12:02')
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E4_stage1_3 AS SELECT * FROM E4_stage1_2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E5 WHERE E4_stage1_2.E4_userid=E5.E5_id)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E1.E1_userid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E3_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E3 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E3.E3_userid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E2.E2_owneruserid)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E5_stage2_0 AS SELECT * FROM E5 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4_stage1_3 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E5.E5_id)

CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E_stage3 AS SELECT E1_stage2_0.E1_userid AS E1_userid, E3_stage2_0.E3_userid AS E3_userid FROM E4_stage1_3, E1_stage2_0, E3_stage2_0, E2_stage2_0, E5_stage2_0 WHERE E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E1_stage2_0.E1_userid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E3_stage2_0.E3_userid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E2_stage2_0.E2_owneruserid AND E4_stage1_3.E4_userid=E5_stage2_0.E5_id
